363
00:28:05,068 --> 00:28:06,763
Oi, Lindsey, voltei.

364
00:28:17,676 --> 00:28:20,406
Você sabe o que fez!

365
00:28:22,148 --> 00:28:25,015
Desculpe. Eu sinto tanto.

366
00:28:25,251 --> 00:28:26,775
